{"tid":871472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Kai] 「佳」字在船上 「香港進」寓意深","createTime":"2018-10-22T03:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T13:48:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"87f2420695d711453bbff3249e88f348e6afba95","tid":871472,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.wenweipo.com/2018/10/22/a05d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.wenweipo.com%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2Fa05d.jpg&h=1c3daede&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華介紹，是次香港館的主題為「香港進」，這個「進」字有豐富的含義，除了解作進口貿易外，亦代表了香港的角色：從來都是國家進出一個最大的門戶，最好的平台；此外，將「進」拆開可見「佳」字在船上，亦可解作香港作為領航船將最好的東西帶入國家，及將國家最好的東西帶出世界；最後，「進」亦有先進、進步及促進的意義。<br />\n<br />\n香港館以「彩帶」作設計概念<br />\n<br />\n商經局披露，港府將於國家貿易投資綜合展內的中國館設立香港地區展示區，展館的面積約126平方米，設計以「彩帶」為概念，配合以多媒體科技，以流轉的動態展現出香港多年來將產品及服務帶進國家。另外還會以OLED透明觸控屏幕、混合實景裝置、全息投影儀器、立體光雕投影、互動圖書及裸眼3D顯示屏等技術，介紹香港的優勢、香港大型基建設施、著名旅遊景點，以及香港產品和發明。<br />\n<br />\n香港地區展示區的主題還包括香港參與「一帶一路」建設、粵港澳大灣區發展、香港於國家改革開放四十年間的貢獻、「一國兩制」及基本法。為了展示香港的獨特文化面貌，在香港地區展示區將會安排「每日亮點」節目，包括口琴小組合奏、無伴奏合唱、中西樂跨界演奏、折子戲及時裝表演。此外，民政事務局於香港和上海招募了香港青年參與進博會的志願工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2018/10/22/FS1810220005.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2FFS1810220005.htm&d=%2B2ToEs93tEd13KwEjqwzm0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=f67fd0df\" target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2018/10/22/FS1810220005.htm</a>"},{"pid":"df77ac0c3987fd9f746c46d42fbf580471980829","tid":871472,"uid":4917,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:41:17.000Z","msg":"進？<br />\n邊撚度進？"},{"pid":"d7dc7055779915eb56417e595850d4aed87442ee","tid":871472,"uid":5739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:54:42.000Z","msg":"個ONG咁似on9..."},{"pid":"9ef5192b2763692a3c6a1ee5ff5daa28080c07b1","tid":871472,"uid":2772,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:56:35.000Z","msg":"卜佳"},{"pid":"b64f8907078da5d3dd15abce97018d7a6b1af02e","tid":871472,"uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5522/29500372154_a4e042e65b_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm6.staticflickr.com%2F5522%2F29500372154_a4e042e65b_o.jpg&h=52d87af4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"018c3febd3e6c2516635593a89104497b630ae6b","tid":871472,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T04:03:08.000Z","msg":"DQ, on9 潛力圖"},{"pid":"da5f14906bc1f91c41f97bfcdde1fb77fb63838f","tid":871472,"uid":51720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T04:03:53.000Z","msg":"香港進 + 開電視 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b36fead98ed7e6b1e375d03323d6520c6b6dc2e","tid":871472,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T04:15:37.000Z","msg":"「兩個ONG」直情倒轉就見到「ON99」添~"},{"pid":"5cee01212ef8ef8cdcd0dd38dedde9e42bc4e40f","tid":871472,"uid":43173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"佳 同 隹 都分唔到，局長讀返小學先啦"},{"pid":"7b59891f6f76c49e5154d6d216982b86bfc558e4","tid":871472,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T13:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Evo4F2W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEvo4F2W.jpg&h=84402096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人D創作真係成舊屎咁，日本仔高好多囉。"},{"pid":"f0d873e2f39d3f57a6494465a88cc9fe78a0cd3d","tid":871472,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T13:48:37.000Z","msg":"坐艇兼仆街仲唔大撚鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}